Package de.unpixelt.locale

Enum Locale

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Locale>
      • de.unpixelt.locale.Locale
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Locale>
    public enum Locale
extends Enum<Locale>
    An enum of all locale codes used by Minecraft which defines the language of the player's client.
    This data comes from the Minecraft fandom page and the official Minecraft translation project.
